&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking talented and motivated &lt;strong&gt;Analyst &lt;/strong&gt;to join the Office of the CEO, working directly with our Manager of the Office of the CEO to drive the strategic and operational priorities of Sezzle&#39;s CEO. This is not a traditional analyst role. You will function as an executive-grade project manager: the person who gets things done across the organization, removes obstacles for leadership, and turns ambiguous directives into clear outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are hiring multiple analysts. The bar is high. We hire ambitious recent graduates with exceptional academic records, high IQ, high EQ, and a relentless drive to deliver. You will sit inside the executive wing, reporting through the Chief of Staff to the CEO, and you will be exposed to the full operational and strategic agenda of a publicly traded fintech (Nasdaq: SEZL) on its path to becoming a bank.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a fast-paced, high-accountability environment. We start compensation modest and reward performance aggressively. Top performers move quickly. Underperformance is addressed directly.&lt;/p&gt;
