&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking for a teammate who can work full-time Tuesday through Saturday between 9:00 am - 5:30 pm - Central Time. This will be a salaried, contractor position.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
